hackathon-description-text: HackISU is a new hackathon for all students at Iowa State University.
hackathon-requirements: You have creative freedom. Make something to wow the judges, who will be focusing on the technical, design, and feasibility of your project.
hackathon-rules:
Don't start your project until the hackathon begins.
Then have at it.

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: $1000 + 3scale API conference tickets + HP Swag Bag

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: How technically challenging is this project?
The design of the project.  Does it look AWESOME?

hackathon-description-header: HackISU is the premiere hackathon for students at Iowa State University. Bring your best ideas and join us for 24 hours of fun, excitement, coding, and prizes.
